07:11.066 --> 07:12.292
Or whatever.

07:12.605 --> 07:13.443
What do you mean?

07:13.475 --> 07:16.073
- Well, I don't believe in God.
- Huh?

07:18.257 --> 07:20.412
Stan? Stan, you okay?

07:21.356 --> 07:23.792
- Atheist!
- Stan, relax.

07:23.958 --> 07:25.322
Why is this
such a big deal?

07:25.366 --> 07:27.292
What? That you're
a Godless heathen?

07:27.336 --> 07:29.230
But we're agreed
about everythig else.

07:29.237 --> 07:32.042
We're both gun-loving,
red meat-eating Republicans

07:32.076 --> 07:35.591
with a passion for paddleboats
that sometimes borderson the erotic.

07:35.638 --> 07:38.320
And we're both Godless heathens.
That's just you!

07:38.405 --> 07:39.882
Look, I'm sorry, Stan,

07:39.915 --> 07:42.873
