I'm trying to disprove.

08:00.937 --> 08:04.033
I am about to show you
irrefutable proof that God exists.

08:04.075 --> 08:07.133
Hey, whatever it takes
to put this whole thing behind us.

08:11.778 --> 08:13.360
Just look at that sunset.

08:13.397 --> 08:17.302
If that's nothing but science,
then why is it so damned romantic?

08:17.908 --> 08:19.773
