08:41.607 --> 08:43.030
Now, that's a miracle.

08:43.065 --> 08:45.111
Well, birth is
an amazing process,

08:45.146 --> 08:47.860
but it's completely
explainable by natural laws.

08:47.996 --> 08:50.982
Okay, I'll give you that.
But look at the vagina!

08:51.027 --> 08:53.970
Look at it stretch.
It's so strong and resilient.

08:54.475 --> 08:56.883
That's what our troops
should be wearing!

08:59.178 --> 09:00.561
Well, here we are.

09:00.608 --> 09:03.251
This is Hogwarts-
the American campus.

09:03.295 --> 09:06.181
I know it doesn't
look like much, but-

09:06.227 --> 09:08.433
