appearance of the school.

09:10.645 --> 09:12.783
You wouldn't understand
how these things work.

09:14.528 --> 09:16.572
Why don't you go bang
on the door real hard?

09:16.616 --> 09:17.871
Let them know
you're here.

09:17.906 --> 09:20.771
Well, have fun with your
regular, boring life, Roger.

09:20.807 --> 09:22.543
I've got magic to learn.

09:23.286 --> 09:25.740
Okay, Steve, how special
are you gonna feel

09:25.777 --> 09:28.190
