invisible dementors?

09:49.788 --> 09:50.752
Shut up!

09:51.768 --> 09:52.973
Potions class!

09:53.017 --> 09:55.652
Did you get all this stuff
from Professor Snape?

09:55.685 --> 09:58.292
You do not freakin' ask
who we got this from!

09:59.075 --> 10:01.002
He Who Shall Not Be Named!

10:01.306 --> 10:03.351
This is Hoppy.
He knows what to do.

10:03.397 --> 10:06.250
My potions partner!
You're my Ron Weasley!

10:06.286 --> 10:07.472
Lavate las manos.

10:07.508 --> 10:08.622
