to me after lights out!

10:42.567 --> 10:44.033
Unspeakable things.

10:44.357 --> 10:45.312
Enough, Stan!

10:45.358 --> 10:46.960
Why is this is such a big deal?

10:47.005 --> 10:49.441
Because, if I can't
make you believe in God,

10:49.488 --> 10:50.600
then you won't
go to heaven,

10:50.646 --> 10:52.861
and I want our friendship
to last forever.

10:52.896 --> 10:54.611
Just picture it.

11:10.187 --> 11:11.231
Thank you, Stan.

11:11.275 --> 11:13.583
Thank you for proving
to me that God exists

11:13.617 --> 11:16.011
so I can have
this awesome after life.

11:16.096 --> 11:18.360
You're the best friend ever.

11:42.686 --> 11:47.061
But the only way it can happen
is if you embrace God.

11:47.097 --> 11:49.573
Look, Stan, I like that
you're close-minded.

11:49.615 --> 11:50.983
It's one of the things
we share,

11:51.015 --> 11:53.393
