accept me for who I am,

11:53.436 --> 11:55.493
then this friendship is over!

11:56.097 --> 11:57.271
Brett, no!

11:57.306 --> 11:58.732
You gotta believe!

11:59.137 --> 12:02.760
Wait! The Lord is my shepherd,
but you're my ride home!

12:14.618 --> 12:18.360
I got your message
that you needed meright now, poolside.

12:18.406 --> 12:21.290
Oh, Father Donovan,
right this way.

12:25.375 --> 12:28.331
Your husband is home
and he's looking right at us.

12:28.378 --> 12:29.940
I- I know he's here.

12:29.976 --> 12:32.310
I called you over
so you could talk to him.

12:32.967 --> 12:37.231
Next time maybe don't end your text message
with a side ways smiley face.

12:37.266 --> 12:38.891
It's very misleading.

12:45.858 --> 12:46.500
What?

12:46.977 --> 12:48.911
I'm having a spiritual crisis.

12:48.946 --> 12:52.022
What do you do when your best
friend doesn't believe in God?

12:52.066 --> 12:54.561
Well, Stan, we're
hardly best friends.

12:54.606 --> 12:56.851
