to burn in hell for all eternity.

13:02.017 --> 13:06.323
Oy! I am so sick of listening
to everyone's problems.

13:06.365 --> 13:10.193
Why do people only come to me
when their live sare in shambles?

13:11.308 --> 13:15.471
Of course! People turn to God
in times of crisis.

13:15.517 --> 13:17.901
If I want to save
Brett's immortal soul,

13:17.938 --> 13:20.191
