$2,000? $2,000?

13:48.666 --> 13:51.912
Yeah, you can have it
if you want.

13:51.955 --> 13:55.131
It's muggle money.
So, now why would I be pissed?

13:56.098 --> 14:00.262
You would be pissed if I forgot
to give you this magic wand.

14:00.706 --> 14:02.802
Wow! It's so light!

14:02.846 --> 14:06.773
I- I can't tell if I'm leading it
or it's leading me.

14:06.977 --> 14:08.931
Oh, is that another one?

14:08.938 --> 14:10.272
No, that's a chop stick.

14:10.955 --> 14:13.330
Look, I've been acting like a jackass.

14:13.567 --> 14:16.083
It was ridiculous of me
to think we had to agree

14:16.117 --> 14:17.523
about every little thing.

14:17.558 --> 14:20.473
That's okay, Stan.
I can't stay mad at you.

14:20.517 --> 14:21.953
That's such a relief.

14:21.988 --> 14:24.123
And as a token of my
unconditional friendship,

14:24.155 --> 14:25.611
