that restaurant.

15:50.295 --> 15:52.203
So, what are you gonna do?

15:52.237 --> 15:54.343
I mean, where will you turn
in this hour of need?

15:54.348 --> 15:55.363
It' gone be ok.

15:55.396 --> 15:58.803
